<hymn_number>5252</hymn_number>
<title>qd ṣʿd ạlrb</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- qad̊ ṣaʿida ạlrãbũ ại̹lay̱ ạảbīhi fī ạl̊maj̊di
 waqad̊ ạảʿadã man̊zilạ lisẖaʿ̊bihi ạl̊maf̊dī̃̊

[V2]
 2- gẖanũwạ biạảl̊ḥāni ạlnãsẖīd̊ lil̊wāʿidi ạlạảmīn̊
 sub̊ḥaⁿạ waḥam̊daⁿạ qadĩmūạ lahu fī kulĩ ḥīn̊

[V3]
 3- sabīlunā yā mū̊̉minūn̊ nasīru biạlại̹ymān̊
 dẖik̊ru ạs̊mi yasūʿa ạl̊ḥanūn̊ yubadĩdu ạlạảḥ̊zān̊

[V4]
 4- sīrūạ bilạ hamiⁿ̃ walạ kẖaẘfiⁿ mina ạlạảʿ̊dā
 waman̊ ạảʿadã ạl̊man̊zila sayun̊jizu ạl̊waʿ̊dā

[V5]
 5- yuqīmu man̊ taḥ̊ta ạltẖãray̱ yugẖayĩru ạlạảj̊sād̊
 yakẖ̊ṭafunā falạ naray̱ maẘtaⁿạ walạ fasād̊

[V6]
 6- nakūnu maʿ̊hu kulã ḥīn̊ fī maj̊dihi ạlrãfīʿ̊
 wabiạlsũrūri nāẓirīn̊ jamālahu ạl̊badīʿ̊</lyrics>
</song>